<div class="container text-center">
  <div class="row gx-5">

<div class="col-12">
      <h3 class="mt-4">Do you need help designing a plan for your patient?</h3>
      </div>

    <div class="col-lg-6 mb-5">
      <p class="mt-2">Now you can ask <em>MassageMentorAI</em> to help you identify any contraindications and recommend a basic plan for your session. Additionally, your helpful assisant will give you some long-term care tips, as well as suggest take-home exercises.</p>
      <small>
        <p class="text-start">Helpful tips:</p>
        <ul class="text-start">
          <li>Be as descriptive as possible - include any conditions, medications, surgeries and anything else you can think of. </li>
          <li>If you are not satisfied with the generated response or forgot to add something, don't worry! You can always ask a follow-up question or add additional information about the patient's medial history. </li>
        </small>
        <ul>

    </div>


<div class="col-lg-6">
<img src="img/chatbot.svg" alt="image of chatbot">
</div>


        <div class="col mt-3">
          <form action="/insert_prompt" method="post" onsubmit="return loadLink()">
            <div class="mb-3 col-lg-8 mx-auto">

              <textarea id="topic_box" name="query_topic" class="form-control" rows="4" cols="30" style="font-size: 17px;" placeholder="Example: 40 year old female, 7 months pregnant. Complains of low back pain that gets worse when sitting at work at her desk. No medications. Diagnosed with gestational diabetes. Doctor recommended massage."></textarea>
            </div>

            <button class="btn btn-primary" type="submit">Submit!</button>
          </form>

<p class="mt-3 text-danger" style="font-size: 12px;">Please note: this tool is designed to offer you a general suggestion in structuring your session. It remains crucial for you to rely on your professional training, experience, and judgment to provide personalized care for your patient. Always adhere to the scope of practice and regulations governing massage therapy in your jurisdiction.</p>

        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <hr>
  <div>
    <div class="container">
    <div><h3>Your past chats:</h3></div>
      <table class="table table-hover table-striped table-fixed align-middle w-100">

        <% @user_prompts.each do |prompt| %>
          <tr class="clickable" onclick="window.location='/prompts/<%= prompt.id %>';">

            <td>
              <%= prompt.topic.truncate(110, separator: ' ') %>
            </td>

            <td class="w-25">
              <%= time_ago_in_words(prompt.created_at) %> ago
            </td>
            
          </tr>
        <% end %>
      </table>
    </div>
  </div>

  <script>
    function loadLink() {
      // Display buffering image
      document.getElementById("loadingText").innerHTML = "MassageMentorAI is generating the chat...";
      // Return true to submit the form
      return true;
    }
  </script>



  <style>
img {
  width: 100%;
  height: auto;
}



  </style>
